00:48:01,000 --> 00:48:03,000
Wait, does Russ not even know what's in the book?

715
00:48:03,000 --> 00:48:04,000
I don't know if he can read his writing, guys.

716
00:48:04,000 --> 00:48:06,000
It's just a blank book.

717
00:48:07,000 --> 00:48:09,000
Did you just say sexy goblin?

718
00:48:10,000 --> 00:48:12,000
How do I just leave?

719
00:48:14,000 --> 00:48:15,000
Well, that's a pickle.

